capture it in the next move.} 22. Rxf6 {Here 22... gxf6 fails to 23.Ng5+} Rxg2+
23. Kf1 Qb5+ (23... Qb5+ $1 {This is the finall killing move.} 24. Rc4 gxf6 $19
